@HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5035

### 200 OK - get all employees
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Accept: application/json

###

### 200 OK - get employee by id
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 BadRequest - invalid id
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/0
Accept: application/json

###

### 404 NotFound - employee does not exist
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/100
Accept: application/json

###

### 201 Created - create a new employee
POST {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Suresh",
  "department": "Finance",
  "salary": 55000
}

###

### 400 BadRequest - invalid POST body
POST {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "department": "Finance",
  "salary": 0
}

###

### 204 NoContent - delete employee
DELETE {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 500 InternalServerError demo
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/server-error-demo
Accept: application/json

###

### Quick summary endpoint
GET {{HttpStatusCodesDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/employees/status-code-summary
Accept: application/json

###
